results.description:
Everyone's favorite wall-crawler in his most unlikely team-up with the "Merc with a mouth"; Deadpool! By the creative team that gave us the first ongoing Deadpool series in 1997, Joe Kelly and Ed McGuinness!

Collected Editions

  • Spider-Man/Deadpool: Isn't It Bromantic (#1-5 & 8)
  • Spider-Man/Deadpool by Joe Kelly & Ed McGuinness (#1-5, 8-10, 13-14 & 17-18)
  • Monsters Unleashed: Battleground (#1.MU)
  • Spider-Man/Deadpool: Side Pieces (#6-7, 11-12 & 1.MU)
  • Spider-Man/Deadpool: Itsy Bitsy (#9-10, 13-14 & 17-18)
  • Deadpool: World's Greatest: 'Till Death Do Us... (#15-16)
  • Deadpool: World's Greatest Volume 4 (#15-16)
  • Spider-Man/Deadpool: Serious Business (#19-22)
  • Spider-Man/Deadpool: Arms Race (#23-28)
  • Spider-Man/Deadpool: WLMD (#29-33)
  • Spider-Man/Deadpool: My Two Dads (#34-39)

Note: Volume named per the indicia.
